            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> lamb skewers</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min on each side or until browned – these are your <strong>Greek-style lamb kebabs</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1678302886009-x200.jpg",
