    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>roast potatoes</strong> to a plate and top with the <strong>oregano</strong> <strong>cucumber salad</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>Greek-style lamb kebabs</strong> to the side and drizzle the <strong>garlic mayo </strong>all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
